        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>
                    <exhotlnk document="../afcs/AFC02906.pdf" bookname="AFC">Print ready (PDF file) copy of the AFC
                        letter
                    </exhotlnk>
                </para>
                <para>International has made an improvement in the routing of the heater return hose which extends
                    radiator life and has implemented a program to retrofit 3200, 4200, 4300, 4400, and 8500 Models in
                    the field.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
